subject: French Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Eugenie Bouchard, 20, needed only 52 minutes to knock out eighth-seeded Angelique Kerber and reach the French Open quarterfinals. Her fellow Canadian Milos Raonic also advanced.
